Mass media: Armed Forces of Ukraine fighters secretly negotiate with Donbas militias from the command
Regular telephone communication has been established on the line of armed confrontation in Donbas.
Fighters of the opposing sides constantly communicate with each other on mobile phones, and this communication is not known in the headquarters.
Fighters of the Armed Forces of Ukraine and Donbas militia have established communication over cellular phones in secret from their high command.
