Warren is a senior fellow in finance at Oxford University.
A spokesman for the university and Somerville College said in an email statement: "We have been in contact with UK police and stand ready to provide any necessary assistance to US investigators."
The statement also said Warren's colleagues are in shock and want him to give up.
Chicago Police Department Communications Chief Anthony Guglielmi said he strongly advised the suspects to turn themselves in.
